15:07.540 --> 15:09.974
What do you have to
say for yourself, Phil?

15:11.744 --> 15:13.444
Where are you going?

15:13.446 --> 15:16.180
What are you doing?

15:16.182 --> 15:17.949
Hey!

15:17.951 --> 15:18.950
Hey!
Hey!

15:18.952 --> 15:19.951
Phil!
Phil!

15:19.953 --> 15:21.286
(knocking)

15:21.288 --> 15:22.954
Oh.

15:22.956 --> 15:25.623
