16:31.624 --> 16:33.524
and-and we're not gonna
negotiate with you

16:33.526 --> 16:35.193
on this, okay?

16:35.195 --> 16:39.163
You know, C to the T,
and... and, uh... such.

16:41.800 --> 16:43.201
Okay, tell you what.

16:43.203 --> 16:44.936
